snippet.title: Dead by Daylight | Tokyo Ghoul Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience Tokyo Ghoul like never before with a terrifying take on Ken Kaneki, the latest Killer to enter The Fog. 

Beyond that, The Tokyo Ghoul Collection features new Outfits for The Ghoul – including a Legendary Rize Kamishiro Outfit – Yui Kimura, Nea Karlsson, Renato Lyra, and more:

The Ghoul – Rize Kamishiro – Legendary
The Ghoul - Awakened Ghoul - Very Rare
Yui Kimura - Rabbit Costume - Very Rare
Nea Karlsson - Eto Costume - Very Rare
Renato Lyra - Hide Costume - Very Rare
Jake Park – Ayato’s Mask
David King – Tatara’s Mask 
The Unknown – Noro’s Mask
Jonah Vasquez – Fukurou’s Mask

Chapter: https://dbd.game/3Ftj4E5
Collection: https://dbd.game/3XCedHe

Trapped forever in a realm of eldritch evil where even death is not an escape, four determined Survivors face a bloodthirsty Killer in a vicious game of nerve and wits. Pick a side and step into a world of tension and terror with horror gaming's best asymmetrical multiplayer.     

PLAY DEAD BY DAYLIGHT: https://buythegame.deadbydaylight.com/   

Join the official forum:  https://forums.bhvr.com/dead-by-daylight/
